Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异母姐妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在同一天出生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲也是同一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不为人所知的秘密姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别多管闲事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再追问了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过刚刚的话要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但小一承受着巨大的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对绝对要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会对任何人说起的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  不知不觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚同学大概也是这种感受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上厕所？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕天女目呢  总感觉你很自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我很自由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说  总觉得你这样很棒就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲刺！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迟到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭是要吃速成咖喱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瑛她很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开朗  又平易近人  真羡慕她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她能那么坚强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹  饭做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是夏祭的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你迷路的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悠送给我的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是母亲的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  已经要出门了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  今天轮到我值日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  悠  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是来得好早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为要换花儿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是悠你来得好早呀  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  我有些事想单独和天女目谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.76,0:06:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…以前见过面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠你果然还记得我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…又来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我真的超开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  能想起来真的好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏祭的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得我们一起去捉知了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说  要抓一只珍奇的知了送给我  然后爬上了树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  连这都被你想起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  这都是多早的事情了  别介意别介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  除此以外再没有母亲别的遗物了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说我连母亲的记忆都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找吧  去找你母亲的挂坠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这个星期天…不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以倒是可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就说定了  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这身打扮是要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事关个人隐私所以我不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谁一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  和亮平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是礼拜天的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:09:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你浑身充满干劲呢  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是天女目  你这身打扮没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得在这前面的杉树
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面  就是我们捉知了的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果弄丢了  就是丢在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我没事先告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候爬的树
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被三年前的水土流失给冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目你在那儿等着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个地方看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要为我做到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说不用做到这种地步的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弄丢挂坠的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然马上露出笑脸对我说  不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当你一个人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你的表情变得很忧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}而最近的那个早晨  我在教室又看到你和那时一样忧伤的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其实一直都藏着忧伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我想让天女目能够一直露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我绝不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:12:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  悠  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  天女目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了  我会尽快洗好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服也没那么快烘干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把浴巾放这了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没听见了  有人进来的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去都是爷爷先泡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再「呀呵」一下走进来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很让人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先洗吧  我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到脸的话会难为情的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去经常像这样坐在爷爷的膝盖上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像碰到很硬的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问什么  就像这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是在做坏事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是悠的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡晕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那肯定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉依姬大人  我做了遭报应的事真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去世了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说不定还在世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一带的孩子全都由我奶奶负责过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会留下什么记录
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有这个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你的母亲可能也很想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人太多  头都要晕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找个地方休息一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等下不是要上台跳舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上场的时候就会认真加油的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初佳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,供奉用的各种物品都准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  准备齐全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来都对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去准备跳舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉依姬是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是供奉在这里的神灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点我还是懂的  我不是问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉依姬是一位喜欢过几名人类的神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人们却无法接受叉依姬的神圣与庄严
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果都离她而去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉依姬把这份悲伤藏在笑容背后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终决定一直默默地为人类的幸福祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这样的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待续
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//--------------------M---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:18.61,title3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}想屡战屡胜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.13,0:22:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦  初佳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只有立直…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实还有三宝牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  算上里宝一共七宝牌！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.69,0:22:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初佳小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八寻姐姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.02,0:22:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  初佳小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会来拯救我吗  悠君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话  那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是犯花痴的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我通过这场对局来占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.88,0:22:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能超过零分  那他对我也有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:22:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还能胜出的话  就能和他顺利交往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能在这里胡出起死回生的役满…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该打哪张好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点吧  瑛  怎么想都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.55,0:23:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋人确定？不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是老公确定？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这种玩法吗  老公
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为游戏里没有这个场景
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是执着的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.39,0:23:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  那里  不能挤…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.29,0:23:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  自摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初佳小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.19,0:23:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的总结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:03.83,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}国破山河在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:03.83,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.20,0:24:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待续
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.46,0:25:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的笑容背后所封闭的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.91,0:25:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算能被明亮地照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.21,0:25:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定会伤害到他人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.33,0:25:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  悠  这样子就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.36,0:25:51.90,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(320,280)}瑛不言弃


